com.guidewire.ab.external.entity

Interface ContactSearchResult

  • All Superinterfaces:
    gw.pl.external.entity.Entity, gw.pl.external.entity.KeyableEntity, Versionable
    Deprecated. 
    External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface ContactSearchResult
extends Versionable, gw.pl.external.entity.Entity
    ContactSearchResult has been deprecated since ClaimCenter 8.0 along with IAddressBookAdapter.

    Represents the set of results and additional information returned by an Address Book search. See the IAddressBookAdapter for information on searching for contacts.
